  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de libdbusmenu-qt</title>

    <para>Installez <application>libdbusmenu-qt</application> en lançant les
    commandes suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd build</userinput></screen>

    <para>Préparez la construction du paquet&nbsp;:</para>
       
<screen><userinput>cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=$(pkg-config --variable=prefix QtCore) .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>
